metadata.name: Hello
metadata.description:
XXX and Drugs.....

That's what this place used to be....

I used to come to the city often  as a kid with my Father, he worked in the NYC garment center then and still does to this day....

I was given strict instructions to never walk past 39th street....

Even when they had phone booths in Times Square you wouldn't dare use them.....

Things have changed for the better here but when I see a phone booth or things from that era it reminds me of simpler times.....

Times when all of my family was here.... times when having change on you was real important and times when I wasn't allowed to walk in Times Square ðŸ˜Š

Photo Taken Aug 28th 2017.
